data.description: Experience pure luxury in this captivating open concept home within The Meadows at McCormick Woods with over 70k in upgrades! The heart of this home is the designer kitchen, a culinary dream featuring pristine white cabinetry, SS appliances, granite countertops + an expansive island. The living room, adorned w/ a gas fireplace is perfect for cozy evenings. Office w/ french doors! Upstairs, the primary suite is your personal retreat w/ a lavish 5-piece en-suite bathroom & a generous walk-in closet. 3 more bedrooms & a family room offer versatility & space for your needs. Covered back patio leads to fully fenced backyard which backs up to a greenbelt, providing privacy & a natural backdrop. New McCormick Village Retail Center coming in 2024!
